{"tid":732179,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得02年世界杯，比利時對巴西入球被判無效","createTime":"2018-07-06T18:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T03:47:57.000Z","uid":132461,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"498152ce33caf2b88ddba7eeac1116064e6f4dfc","tid":732179,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:53:37.000Z","msg":"2002年06月19<br />\n<br />\n韋莫斯不接受球證道歉<br />\n隨球隊在十六強輸給巴西出局，比利時教練韋斯基宣布請辭，並會重返比利時甲組標準烈治掌帥。此外，比利時隊長韋莫斯透露，在對巴西一仗判其上半場頭槌入球無效的球證柏蘭達加斯，看過電視重播知道自己判錯後，半場休息時曾向他道歉，但韋莫斯怒言不會接受道歉。綜合外電（日本）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20020619/2666914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020619%2F2666914&d=KwQRTlZNBeVuro%2BWspPi0B4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=9db8c51d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20020619%2F2666914&h=d6d639a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/daily/article/20020619/2666914</a>"},{"pid":"866857634639cc570ac4dcad1e11ea22647fec47","tid":732179,"uid":132461,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:55:06.000Z","msg":"今次巴西係還債"},{"pid":"539c7d630db59310e0cec22577e3ab7ed8538c72","tid":732179,"uid":132461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcda622478b37b97d2ce3020dc0b10477b732de","tid":732179,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"當年的卡斯拿斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0998f4d94b2154c1ddfcddb4de7cb041c01fc44","tid":732179,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:52:08.000Z","msg":"02年真係黑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fif